          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Pt Cabello</placeName>
                                        <date>Novr 14 1853</date>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <addressee>Isaac Leeser Esqr</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">
                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">Dear Sir,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Your esteemed favor per “Pair” dated <date>27
                                                  July</date> last<lb/> has been received, and I
                                        thank you for the <date>July</date> number<lb/> forwarded at
                                        the same time, of which the different copies have<lb/> been
                                        distributed as requested. I also beg to thank you for<lb/>
                                        the information respecting the Hebrew Grammar and
                                        Dic„<lb/>„tionaries, the cost of which $9.— I remit to you
                                        by <persName>Captain<lb/> Wilkins</persName> of the above
                                        named Barque.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">My latest trip to
                                                  <placeName><sic>Curacoa</sic></placeName> has been
                                        of material<lb/> benefit to my health, which has
                                        considerably improved,<lb/> and I am in hopes of entirely
                                        regaining strength and health<lb/> by following the
                                        directions of the physician I consulted.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Thanking you for your kind attention and
                                                  <sic>enquiries</sic><lb/> I remain as ever</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">Yours sincerely</p>
                              <p rend="indent(10)">
                                        <persName role="author">A Myerston</persName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Isaac Leeser Esqr</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">
                                        <placeName>
                                                  <hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi>
                                        </placeName>
                              </p>
                              <p>with $9.—</p>
                    </body>
